A floral decoration commemorating the eternal
connection of friendship. It's an event item.

If two people who share a wish ring it together,
their wish will come true. It's an event item.

For Heroes who like to deepen their bonds
over tea or at gatherings. It's an event item.

Used in Aether Raids to build structures that
are available for a limited time. If that period
has elapsed, these stones will be lost.
